@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ibfgzv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.exp((v1 + 0.10 * v0 + 0.38)))
    v0 = wp.exp(((v0 + 0.61 + v2 + 0.10) + (tmp + 0.66 / v0 + 0.16)))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.exp(wp.sin(v2 + 0.40)))
    data[tid] = v0
